---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Backyard Sauna Pro"
  description="Backyard Sauna Pro is an independent review site helping homeowners find the best outdoor saunas for their space and budget."
  canonical="/about"
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">About Backyard Sauna Pro</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      Backyard Sauna Pro is an independent resource for homeowners who are serious about adding a sauna to their property. We cover buying guides, product reviews, installation tips, and maintenance advice without the fluff.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      Our goal is simple: give you the same advice a knowledgeable friend in the sauna industry would give you. That means honest pros and cons, real price context, and no sugarcoating on products that aren't worth your money.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-3">How We Make Money</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      This site earns revenue through affiliate commissions. When you click a product link and make a purchase on Amazon or other retailers, we may receive a small commission at no extra cost to you. This is how we keep the lights on and the content free.
    </p>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">
      Our affiliate relationships do not influence which products we recommend. We only recommend products we believe are genuinely worth considering.
    </p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600">
      Have a question, a product suggestion, or a correction? <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-700 underline">Get in touch</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
